.SH "NAME"
rofi-blezz \- Run rofi in blezz mode.
.SH "SYNOPSIS"
.sp
\fIrofi\-blezz\fP [menu] [config] [rofi args]
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
.sp
Runs rofi in blezz mode with different starting \fImenu\fP.
This is a workaround for rofi\(cqs blezz module not having an equivalent for
blezz\(cqs \f(CR\-d\fP option.
.sp
The \f(CR$ROFI_BLEZZ_THEMESTR\fP environment variable will be applied to rofi\(cqs
theme. The default is \fIentry {placeholder:"Press hotkey";}\fP .
